  "text": "In recent years, increasing evidence indicates a link between acne and exposure to environmental pollutants through unclear mechanisms [CITATION_1] . Our data elaborate the molecular mechanisms of AhR -a transcription factor that senses environmental stimuli to regulate innate immunity in human SZ95 sebocytes -and provide a new insight into the association between environment pollution and regulation of innate immunity in acne.",
